s://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AdYd0SZNs-c&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n00後會話 我唔識the room"},{"pid":"ec632900c5a5f16d027a9916a2e5dc66d2c05caf","tid":615632,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:47:38.000Z","msg":"00後援交妹，俾你屌都大大力屌啦"},{"pid":"97587c210dcf36304c1233deb229141a1d4370cb","tid":615632,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"688b1a1a62cf95e7000612d99212ea53e6c12412","tid":615632,"uid":41943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:50:44.000Z","msg":"引用：#1961524 &bull; 1-21<br />\n唔係老屎忽嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以往屌鳩80後90後，係話佢哋冇責任感唔上進嬌生慣養等等根本係普遍後生仔嘅共同點。<br />\n<br />\n但依家00後就直程同8090後斷層，講蝗語玩蝗app睇蝗劇，完全冇本土意識，呢點係8090後從來未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n編輯"},{"pid":"0321e3cd3293418f3cb88e0b6c632d4126ddfb3b","tid":615632,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6503f04b6a2ce12ff1d5eaaf6753a4315e1983c","tid":615632,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:53:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f66bc71e065f60eb0fb4e0792ca8be2362d255c","tid":615632,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:54:22.000Z","msg":"其實有冇諗過反共嘅係小部份人，根本你地先係異類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5caa86fd8deb2b9401c0a7fa163d71d3fdd4a3a","tid":615632,"uid":41943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:54:22.000Z","msg":"212Commitment &bull; 1-21<br />\n諗深入啲其實好撚悲觀<br />\n香港文化，包括樂壇同電影<br />\n最光輝年代一定係80後個時期<br />\n而90後都算係趕尾班車接觸到呢啲文化<br />\n至少周星馳、古惑仔、陳奕迅等等都肯定仲係家傳戶曉<br />\n但係去到00後香港文化真係末落得好緊要<br />\n你數到有咩香港文化產物係呢幾年間出到名？<br />\n坤哥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以都唔係話怪曬啲00後<br />\n而係香港整體文化實力問題<br />\n比起韓國 甚至中國都係輸一大截"},{"pid":"52bce0593a2a2da89f5304f82b14bce5c74610a6","tid":615632,"uid":41943,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c6503f04b6a2ce12ff1d5eaaf6753a4315e1983c","tid":615632,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:53:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:55:15.000Z","msg":"所以00後都有點兒可憐"},{"pid":"3a998d77bf9cd80564fb6ccd7874e0546cad73ab","tid":615632,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:56:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9dd2b4e255b394716de2d95472cb931f96b7701b","tid":615632,"uid":41943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"但係00後依然on9"},{"pid":"9f41bc5191b59b0a941fd5cdc34f99e8cdef57ce","tid":615632,"uid":41943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a998d77bf9cd80564fb6ccd7874e0546cad73ab","tid":615632,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:56:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"大台親中"},{"pid":"53899c7ae290b80089d4b516598dc5a18ad4e873","tid":615632,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"465a5297c98d9d817976f84c145d49b43a7d4312","tid":615632,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:59:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3075db9ab3157d06d466d798d604b2119b62718c","tid":615632,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"真心我哋90/80後要諗個方法教佢哋<br />\n<br />\n唔係佢哋只會覺得我哋好似宜家啲老屎窟咁"},{"pid":"4fff50fd4474ccc83308a7103569f9290a51b0d1","tid":615632,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T15:01:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1109997e41d61496f89cef2826d82ac1ded463bd","tid":615632,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor